    • Constructor Detail

      • IHDRChunk

        public IHDRChunk()
        Construct a new uninitialized IHDR chunk. This constructor is for use only by object deserialization.

      • IHDRChunk

        public IHDRChunk(int width,
         int height,
         int bitDepth,
         int colorType)
        Construct a new IHDR chunk. The following fields are fixed: compression method = 0 (deflate), filter method = 0 (adaptive filtering), interlace method = 0 (no interlacing).
        Parameters:
        width - Image width in pixels.
        height - Image height in pixels.
        bitDepth - Sample bit depth.
        colorType - Color type.
